---
import Section from '@/components/common/Section.astro';

import { type NavItem } from '@/constants/navItems';

interface Props {
	navItem: NavItem;
}

const { navItem } = Astro.props;
---

<Section
	id={navItem.label}
	title="Rides and Shows at Disneyland Resort">
	<p>
		Enjoy classic&nbsp;attractions&nbsp;like Pirates of the Caribbean, the
		Haunted Mansion, the&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/attractions/disneyland/mad-tea-party/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Mad Tea Party</a
		>’s whirling teacups and the&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/attractions/disneyland/matterhorn-bobsleds/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Matterhorn Bobsleds</a
		>&nbsp;ride, as well as experiences featuring new innovations, like the
		incredible special effects, freefall thrills, and multiple storylines of
		the&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/attractions/disney-california-adventure/guardians-galaxy-mission-breakout/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Guardians of the Galaxy Mission: Breakout!</a
		>&nbsp;adventure. Just outside the Breakout! ride, don’t be surprised
		when the music starts pumping and you can join either Team Starlord or
		Team Gamora in a dance-off.
	</p>
	<p>
		Fans of one particular galaxy far, far away will be transported by
		the&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/star-wars-galaxys-edge/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			><em>Star Wars</em>: Galaxy’s Edge</a
		>&nbsp;land, where they can step into the world of Darth Vader and Luke
		Skywalker to live out their own&nbsp;<em>Star Wars</em>&nbsp;storyline,
		flying the Millennium Falcon and exploring a distant outpost. Marvel
		Comics fans won’t want to miss the&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/destinations/disney-california-adventure/avengers-campus/?CMP=ILC-DPFY21Q3wo0408210414210002C"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Avengers Campus</a
		>, the new land dedicated to discovering, recruiting, and training the
		next generation of super heroes. The attraction is also home to the
		Ancient Sanctum, where Dr. Strange emerges from an interdimensional
		portal to enlist the audience’s help in his otherworldly endeavors.
		Families with smaller kids should not miss&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/destinations/disneyland/mickeys-toontown/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Mickey’s Toontown</a
		>, which offers interactive experiences, green spaces for free play, and
		the&nbsp;<a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/attractions/disneyland/mickey-minnies-runaway-railway/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			>Mickey &amp; Minnie’s Runaway Railway</a
		>&nbsp;ride, which has no age or height restrictions.
	</p>
	<p>
		Fantasyland Theatre is another place where you’ll be transported, this
		time to the savannas of Africa via <a
			href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/entertainment/disneyland/tale-of-the-lion-king/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="nofollow"
			><em>Tale of the Lion King</em></a
		>. In this 30-minute theatrical adaptation of the classic Disney movie,
		you’ll follow Simba’s journey by way of narration, choreography, and
		song as he ascends to the throne.
	</p>
</Section>
